&lt;h2 id=&#34;hexoæ’ä»¶hexo-filter-lqip&#34;&gt;hexoæ’ä»¶hexo-filter-lqip&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-filter-lqip&#34;&gt;hexo-filter-lqip&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Hexo plugins which helps to introduce low quality image placeholders to the theme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ä¸æ”¯æŒhexo5.xä»¥ä¸Šç‰ˆæœ¬ï¼Œå¯ä»¥å¼ºåˆ¶å®‰è£… &lt;code&gt;-f&lt;/code&gt;ï¼Œå®ç°æ–¹æ³•å¯ä»¥å€Ÿé‰´&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;Installation&#34;&gt;Installation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-bash&#34; data-language=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token function&#34;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; i hexo-filter-lqip --save&lt;span aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;line-numbers-rows&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;Usage-5&#34;&gt;Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install this plugin for the theme and use the view helper to render a placeholder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;lqipFor-view-helper&#34;&gt;lqipFor view helper&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-none&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-none&#34;&gt;lqipFor(path_to_asset, options)&lt;span aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;line-numbers-rows&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;String&lt;/strong&gt; *path_to_asset - a path to the image&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Object&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;options&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;String&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;[type]&lt;/em&gt; - a type of placeholder, see the list of &lt;a target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-filter-lqip#available-types&#34;&gt;available types&lt;/a&gt;, defaults to the &lt;code&gt;default_type&lt;/code&gt; as configured&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Returns a CSS value for &lt;code&gt;background-image&lt;/code&gt; property, which is a simplified version of the original image.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Example for EJS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-markup&#34; data-language=&#34;markup&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markup&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;div&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;token special-attr&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-name&#34;&gt;style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token attr-value&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation attr-equals&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token value css language-css&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token property&#34;&gt;background-image&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;%- lqip_&lt;span class=&#34;token function&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token string&#34;&gt;&#39;/content/my-photo.jpg&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; %&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token tag&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;div&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;line-numbers-rows&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
